ZaykaExpress
ZaykaExpress is a food delivery web application inspired by Swiggy, designed to provide a seamless food ordering experience with real-time restaurant listings, menu browsing, and order placement.

Features
🍔 Restaurant Listings: Fetch and display nearby restaurants.
📜 Menu Display: View restaurant menus with item details.
🔍 Search Functionality: Search restaurants based on location.
⚡ Shimmer Effect: Smooth UI with loading placeholders.
🌐 Routing with React Router: Seamless page navigation.
📦 State Management: Using Redux Toolkit for global state handling.
🎨 Tailwind CSS: Modern, responsive UI styling.
Tech Stack
Frontend: React, React Router, Redux Toolkit
Styling: Tailwind CSS
APIs: Swiggy Unofficial API (via proxy)
Icons & Fonts: FontAwesome, React Icons
Installation & Setup
Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/mealrush.git
cd mealrush
Install dependencies:
npm install
Start the development server:
npm start
Open the app in your browser at http://localhost:3000.
Folder Structure
ZaykaExpress/
│── src/
│   ├── components/       # Reusable UI components
│   ├── pages/            # Page components (Home, Menu, etc.)
│   ├── redux/            # Redux store and slices
│   ├── assets/           # Images, icons, static files
│   ├── App.js            # Main App component
│   ├── index.js          # Entry point
│── public/
│── package.json
│── tailwind.config.js
│── README.md
API Endpoints
Restaurant List: https://foodfire.onrender.com/api/restaurants?lat={lat}&lng={lng}
Menu Data: https://foodfire.onrender.com/api/menu?restaurantId={id}
